now\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"his oats\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone in the village - which has produced two two-time Olympians - was at pains to say how unassuming the 23-year-old swimmer is.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"two two-time Olympians\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"pains\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"the 23-year-old swimmer\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And many said they had a connection with the family, albeit some more tenuous than others.\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a connection\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I swam with her once at Streedagh on Christmas Day.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Streedagh\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"Christmas Day\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had legs like a thoroughbred horse,\\\" said Sarah Gilroy, a native of Co Sligo now based in Germany.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\", \"score\": 0.999633554962048, \"rank\": 0.0003285682667033199, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\"}, {\"begin\": 908, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norman_Gilroy\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.564722737178192e-12, \"text\": \"Gilroy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norman_Gil