om\": 1038, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She put a lot effort into it from day one.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot effort\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She may go further.\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We would like to see her come home with a gold,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heather Henry, who confessed that as \\\"a blow-in\\\" she did not really know Mona, was nevertheless moved to tears by the local woman's success in the pool in Paris.\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1312, \"end\": 1316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Vanderwaal\", \"score\": 0.999999627106787, \"rank\": 3.728933923017316e-07, \"text\": \"Mona\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Vanderwaal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Vanderwaal\"}, {\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999745341, \"rank\": 2.5246254859164116e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Heather Henry\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"a blow-in\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"the local woman's success\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's absolutely brilliant.\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Afte