.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mona McSharry\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"a bond\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2335}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic medallist\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They go to swimming lessons in Ballyshannon so they love that side of it.\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2397, \"end\": 2409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ballyshannon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.756051095658162e-30, \"text\": \"Ballyshannon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ballyshannon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ballyshannon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimming lessons\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"that side\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be a great buzz for everyone for a while,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great buzz\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jason Currid's claim to fame is that he once worked alongside the Olympian on a job at Lissadell House.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2504, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Grimshaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999687493077, \"rank\": 3.125007968445288e-08, \"text\": \"Jason\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Grimshaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Grimshaw\"}, {\"begin\": 2570, \"end\": 2578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.999999971927537, \"rank\": 2.80722993815386e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2591, \"end\": 2606, \"titl